{"tid":1704189,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請大家一齊罷食呢間偽黃 黑心老闆只想搵錢","createTime":"2019-11-10T15:02:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T13:00:48.000Z","uid":207766,"like":20,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"36dd07405bae2273d41b13054594c63de0f69c2f","tid":1704189,"uid":207766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T15:02:56.000Z","msg":"利申問人借ac<br />\n我要揭發嘅就係呢間成日自稱本地小店嘅 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">Beans荳子</span></span><br />\n可能大家連聽都冇聽過<br />\n但佢係荃灣起家 沙田 馬鞍山 popcorn 大埔都有分店<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bGWUpu0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbGWUpu0.jpg&h=7049fa35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">罪症1 黑心老闆唔理員工安全 搵錢最緊要</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n係呢幾個月嘅抗爭入面大家都知黑警幾痴線 成日亂尻咁放催淚彈<br />\n話說早幾個月嘅時候同樣係夜晚有活動<br />\n有間分店就有個<span style=\"color: red;\">大肚婆</span>嘅家姐因為擔心佢危險<br />\n早咗<span style=\"color: red;\">一個鐘</span>嚟接佢收工<br />\n鋪頭其他同事都叫佢走先 因為佢住係首都<br />\n但係都要打俾上面講聲 交代下 <br />\n點知個仆街老闆就話<span style=\"color: red;\">早一個鐘差得幾多</span> 唔撚俾佢走<br />\n但講緊個時已經放緊催淚彈 popo亂咁拉緊人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁荃灣就係街鋪嚟嘅 對正大馬路 經常有示威活動<br />\n咁有一次經理就打俾老闆問<br />\n咩情況之下可以close 或者俾同事走先<br />\n點知個仆街老闆就話<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">你要知道 我地唔係一間要賺錢嘅機構<br />\n你連間鋪都睇唔好 點做經理</span><br />\n事後幾次出面大馬路已經勁多狗 放催淚彈<br />\n都唔俾早啲Close<br />\n<br />\n亦都唔會主動提出俾冇車搭嘅員工早啲收工<br />\n<br />\n罪症二-偽黃<br />\n老細成日<span style=\"color: red;\">聲稱</span>自己多次出去發夢<br />\n捐咗幾多錢俾612 星火<br />\n但冇諗過要罷市<br />\n你係你口講嘅咁深黃 點解唔罷？<br />\n講到尾只係一個商人<br />\n佢絕對唔會主動話唔開門 或者俾早啲close<br />\n你如果咁啱見到佢冇開 都係因為員工自發集體罷工<br />\n或者個商場唔開/要求要早啲close<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vwje82q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVwje82q.png&h=c89243b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n真係咁黃 聽日就罷市啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你間嘢都唔平 半價咗啲學生未必負擔得起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果我講大話 我俾人捉入新屋嶺雞姦<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><br />\n雙十一 大三罷<br />\n兄弟爬山  一齊努力<br />\n光復香港 時代革命</strong></span>"},{"pid":"9928f8c9f8d2737b1cebb74467b8daa20aff3f64","tid":1704189,"uid":126621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T15:03:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jM9yEVS.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjM9yEVS.gif&h=36baf129&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"232dc6a91e4b2ca25bf986223f7b4551ca0ac1a7","tid":1704189,"uid":191271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T15:05:10.000Z","msg":"扮黃<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/HKIP2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHKIP2&d=%2FSZuxPcvMLfRWwfRMm0dxO9%2By3EgolabMfI9ImFPBT4%3D&h=1cb66302\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/HKIP2</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ws9KMEO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fws9KMEO.jpg&h=ae373530&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">Hong Kong Independence Party <br />\n5 agendas </span></strong><br />\n<br />\n(1)  UK has the mandate from the People of Hong Kong to annul the Sino-British Joint Declaration right away; Also should the US subsequently abolish the HK Policy Act.<br />\n<br />\n(2) the UK and the US governments are requested by the Hongkongers for taking on the PRC&rsquo;s illegal occupation of Hong Kong.<br />\n<br />\n(3)  We require the United Kingdom to enforce those three unterminated treaties over Hong Kong sovereignty ( the Treaty of Nanking; the Convention of Peking; the Second Convention of Peking ).<br />\n<br />\n(4) We demand Anglo-American or Nato joint military base in Hong Kong on a permanent basis, the expense of which will be covered by ourselves!<br />\n<br />\n(5) Hong Kong should and is going to be an independent Commonwealth nation.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"h