kgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a682adf33497fee0c58624f5084472578a078f56","tid":1704189,"uid":68587,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T06:02:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />朋友做過beans，佢話之前有分店係鋪頭入面癡文宣係當眼處，比腦細見到屌到仆街<br />\n仲好意思話自己係黃，85個日大罷工都係員工自發性罷工先唔開門，事後仲要扣人勞工假"},{"pid":"fd5ca2fcf7da24c42b80cd4ea09d237ccdd787b0","tid":1704189,"uid":98603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T06:04:24.000Z","msg":"德福都就快開新店<br />\n要罷食"},{"pid":"3b02c8ad70cb2c6aa525d032f9ab8f31a8657494","tid":1704189,"uid":105707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T14:08:05.000Z","msg":"8月5沙田店比地方比水比人休息<br />\n但其實全部都係比水喉水人飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講緊係萬年都唔洗個啲水喉<br />\n利申發夢聽到，講大話死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26716e9a9e8ec5f93fca0fec975edc2fc93e9de3","tid":1704189,"uid":278199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T14:25:54.000Z","msg":"聽講佢今日無開？<br />\n係咪因為比人岀post屌完先做樣唔開？"},{"pid":"7298d03d9255dcd2fac363fa7e3cb61af9cb47ce","tid":1704189,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T13:00:48.000Z","msg":"屌你老母<br />\n中大打到死<br />\n叫人做facial <br />\n仆街死啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fU9OKn0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfU9OKn0.png&h=f39fe89b&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}